flowchart TB
  DEV[Developer / Copilot / Agents] --> PR[Pull Request]

  subgraph REPO[Per-Repo (x40+)]
    TPL[PR Template\n(CLAIM tokens + Scope + Evidence Paths)]
    MEM[.eva-memory.json]
    EVD[.eva/evidence/*\n(reports, audits, coverage)]
    CI[Repo CI\n(policy-linter + claim-validator + bootstrap)]
  end

  PR --> TPL
  PR --> CI
  MEM --> CI
  EVD --> CI

  subgraph GOVPOLICY[Central Policy]
    MAP[claim-evidence-map.json]
    SCH[claim-evidence-map.schema.json]
    BUNDLE[Enforcement Bundle\n(manifest + deploy script)]
    LIFE[Lifecycle Rules\n(active/deprecated/removed)]
  end

  GOVPOLICY --> CI

  subgraph REG[Evidence Registry (Git repo)]
    WCAG[WCAG Audit Packs]
    GCDS[GC-DS Compliance Packs]
    I18N[Bilingual Evidence Packs]
    PROV[provenance.json\n(origin + freshness)]
  end

  REG --> CI

  subgraph TELEMETRY[Governance Telemetry]
    AGG[Daily Aggregator Job]
    MET[governance-metrics.json]
    DASH[Dashboards\n(Power BI / reports)]
  end

  CI -->|Results| AGG
  AGG --> MET
  MET --> DASH

  subgraph LIFECYCLE[Policy Evolution]
    DEPREC[Deprecation Engine\nwarn -> soft-fail -> hard-fail]
    MIG[Migration PR Generator]
  end

  LIFE --> DEPREC
  DEPREC --> MIG
  MIG --> PR

  subgraph GCCTRL[GC Controls Integration]
    ATO[ATO Package Builder]
    AIRA[AIRA/EARB Evidence Export]
  end

  MET --> ATO
  MET --> AIRA
  CI --> ATO
  CI --> AIRA
